<placeName cert="high">Oxyrhynchus</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><div n="r" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Ἀ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">πία Ζωίλωι τ</supplied>ῶι 

    <lb n="2"/>ἀδελφῶι χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="3"/>πρὸ πάντων εὔχομαί σε ὑγι-

    <lb n="4"/>αίνειν. ἐρωτηθεὶς, ἄδελφέ, 

    <lb n="5"/>Σαραπίωνα μὴ ἀφῇς ἀργεῖν 

    <lb n="6"/>καὶ ῥέμβεσθαι, ἀλλὰ εἰς <subst><add place="inline">ἐργασί-

    <lb n="7"/>αν</add><del rend="corrected"><del rend="erasure">το<gap extent="3" reason="illegible" unit="character"/></del>αν</del></subst> αὐτὸν βάλε. ἐγὼ μὲν 

    <lb n="8"/>τοῦς ἄρτους <choice><corr>ἐποίησα</corr><sic>εποησα</sic></choice>. πέμψω δέ 

    <lb n="9"/>σοι διὰ Πτολεμ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">αίου ὅτα</supplied>ν αὐτὸς ὁ 

    <lb n="10"/>Πτολεμαῖος λάβ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ῃ. ἄσπασα</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ι</unclear> Μο-

    <lb n="11"/>δεστᾶν καὶ τὸν υἱόν. <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">παρ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear>δώσεις 

    <lb n="12"/>δὲ καὶ τῷ Μοδεστᾷ <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἀφ᾽</supplied> ὧν ἐὰν 

    <lb n="13"/>κ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ο</supplied>μισθῇ σοι. διὰ <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">π</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">αντ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὸς</unclear> ἔχε 

    <lb n="14"/>τ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὸ</supplied>ν Σαραπίωνα ἐπ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ιμ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ελ</unclear>ῶς. 

    <lb n="15"/>ἄ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">σπ</supplied>ασαι καὶ Ἑρμι<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ό</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">νην</supplied> καὶ Ἡρα-

    <lb n="16"/>κ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">λείδ</supplied>ην καὶ τὸν <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">υἱὸ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ν</unclear> αὐτοῦ. 

    <lb n="17"/>ἀ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">σπά</supplied>ζεταί σε καὶ Σ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">αρα</supplied>πίωνα 

    <lb n="18"/><gap extent="7" reason="lost" unit="character"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ι</unclear>ς καὶ ὁ <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">πατή</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ρ</unclear> μου <gap extent="3" reason="illegible" unit="character"/> 
